questions.quote: Hey Doc, check this out. [does an around-the-world with the Yo-Yo]
Hey, where, where are you going? You gonna take a trip? The map... what...
Hi, George. How ya feeling? Is anybody getting your apartment?
I think I'd be good at that. I talk to people all the time. Someone even told me once they thought I'd be a good talk show host.
Cancel!  Think again, longshanks! I started planning this in nineteen seventy-eight. I put a deposit down on that revolving restaurant that overlooks Times Square, and I booked Christopher Cross.
Yes, but you're still not allowed. These seats are very expensive.
Hi, this is Darren from Kramer's office. Mr. Kramer would like to schedule a lunch with you at Monk's coffee shop.
Yes I am, a guy on my mail route just got a couple of tickets and he offered one to me.
The only time it wasn't uncomfortable was when we were making fun of you.
George. Thanks for coming down to talk to me. I wanted to see you right away, but my hours here aren't very flexible. I just started yesterday.
